{"tid":693640,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"有無人因為自己樣貌條件差而好憎靚仔?","createTime":"2018-06-07T15:29:45.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-09T13:50:17.000Z","uid":157510,"like":119,"dislike":30,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"a7d6a413a9233226a3fbde1aa4c1000aaee0277d","tid":693640,"uid":157510,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-07T15:29:45.000Z","msg":"每次見到啲靚仔我心情都特別忟<br />\n<br />\n無他，因為阿媽真係生得我好樣衰<br />\n<br />\n連登仔平日笑稱既窮矮柒毒我基本上樣樣都中哂<br />\n<br />\n但我無因為咁而自怨自艾。相反，我仲化卑憤為力量<br />\n<br />\n每日辛勤工作，做事盡心盡力<br />\n<br />\n終於有一日，經理賞識我，將我由執枱仔升到企收銀位兼水吧位<br />\n<br />\n你班食屎狗靚仔平時唔係好威既咩?<br />\n<br />\n想飲可樂少冰?飲冰水啦柒頭!<br />\n<br />\n依家邊個威啲呀?吓?"},{"pid":"1a9ac636a47811ab7dbc007c182a727fe21a1c9c","tid":693640,"uid":147194,"like":28,"dislike":0,"score":28,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-07T15:31:06.000Z","msg":"3/10"},{"pid":"f65a687975c08b6eddf4951c273dad523caa9bc0","tid":693640,"uid":179571,"like":0,"dislike":6,"score":-6,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-06-07T15:31:58.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"73f6fc506c78b574983054db9153ef4f231fafa2","tid":693640,"uid":150400,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-07T15:32:37.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"e50f0c4b4901d606993c77d3752c457fb2a99659","tid":693640,"uid":89608,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-07T15:33:44.000Z","msg":"只要努力, 窮撚都會有出頭天"},{"pid":"3583d001499d737370c13aef2079fb90e0f558a4","tid":693640,"uid":146558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-07T15:35:10.000Z","msg":"閱"},{"pid":"b76f007e43e201ba1d088fb8edeef6f04a7e78d9","tid":693640,"uid":157510,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f65a687975c08b6eddf4951c273dad523caa9bc0","tid":693640,"uid":179571,"like":0,"dislike":6,"score":-6,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-06-07T15:31:58.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-07T15:45:47.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">悲憤</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">靚囝</span><br />\n<br />\n我柒到連字都打錯<img src=\"